{"tid":1622472,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如何有效地幫助罷工","createTime":"2019-10-04T16:22:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T16:23:34.000Z","uid":292807,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"8a5e2b2a040d7c96973a20a687c478a2083aa2bb","tid":1622472,"uid":292807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T16:22:06.000Z","msg":"今日去到觀塘站發現其實封站係好撚易，成個過程只需5分鐘<br />\n<br />\n只要:<br />\n大概10個勇武+20-30個和理非(越多越好)<br />\n<br />\n勇武負責裝修<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />包括灑水、問候閘大大、檢查滅火筒有無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n和理非負責睇水、做戲、cover勇武<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n勇武最緊要hit &amp; run<br />\n和理非要幫佢地疏散人群，扮曬驚咁<br />\n<br />\n然後就可以橋埋雙手等黨鐵自動波進行不合作運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">好似今日咁每個站朝頭早都咁搞法，各位港豬就想翻都翻唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">到今時今日，和理非罷工真係刻不容緩，大家快d比個藉口佢地長期罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"0278507c122e0017a24398b9277c293437f11ccd","tid":1622472,"uid":292807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T16:23:34.000Z","msg":"認同請幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}